        '看第 23 句：Expertise reduces anchoring effects to some degree in domains with rapid, unambiguous feedback。这里状语在句末，结论（expertise reduces effects）居前，「限定范围」（in domains with rapid feedback）居后，略显松散。对比第 24 句的处理：In domains where feedback is delayed, ambiguous, or contaminated by the decision itself, the anchor\'s pull persists even as the professional\'s confidence in their own judgment grows。把 in domains where… 推到句首，读者一开始就知道「我们在谈哪类情境」，主句的判断（the anchor\'s pull persists）落下时便没有歧义。同时，句末追加的 even as 状语从句（即便信心在增长）成了一个额外的反转，形成「确立范围→断言结果→揭示反直觉的附加细节」三层递进。',
